are widely accepted, the debate heats up when it comes to food and agriculture.

4
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:19,680
Why is that? Why is the same thing treated so differently?

5
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:27,040
Let's try to get to the bottom of this and explore the facts, the fears, and the future of GMOs.

6
