00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:58,880
from the very beginning. GM plants that are destined to be eaten are checked for possible

29
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:05,040
dangers and the results are evaluated by multiple agencies. After more than 30 years and thousands

30
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:10,960
of studies, the science is in. Eating GMO plants is no more risky than their non-GMO equivalent.

