like fruit with higher antioxidant levels that help to fight diseases or rice with additional

69
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:59,280
vitamins. On a larger scale, we're trying to engineer plants that are more resilient to

70
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:04,560
climate change. Plants that can better adapt to erratic weather and adverse soil conditions,

71
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:10,800
making them resistant to droughts or floods. GMOs could also not only reduce agriculture's

72
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:16,160
impact on the environment, but actively help to protect it. Scientists are working on crops that

73
