can draw nitrogen from the air like microbes. Nitrogen is a common fertilizer, but its buildup

74
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:27,920
pollutes the groundwater and speeds up climate change. Plants that collect their own nitrogen

75
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:33,360
could fix two problems at once. The overuse of fertilizers in the developed world, as well as

76
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:38,480
the shortage of it in developing countries. We could even modify plants to become super

